    "zh-TW": "MEMTRACE_TOKEN 匿名行為",
    "en": "MEMTRACE_TOKEN Anonymous Behavior"
  },
  "content": {
    "type": "factual",
    "format": "markdown",
    "body": {
      "zh-TW": "若未傳遞 `MEMTRACE_TOKEN`，系統將維持匿名行為，僅能存取公開工作區，`list_workspaces` 將返回公開庫或空列表。",
      "en": "If `MEMTRACE_TOKEN` is not provided, the system will maintain anonymous behavior, allowing access only to public workspaces. `list_workspaces` will return public repositories or an empty list."
    }
